Prompt — Map Completion Strategy: Iterative Blender Modeling

We are building a 3D open walkthrough of Central Park in Godot. The map currently uses billboard/sprite placeholders for many structures throughout the park. We want to replace all of these with proper 3D models built iteratively in Blender using the bpy Python scripting API.
