Favor Blender modifiers (Array, Mirror, Bevel, Solidify, Curve, Displace) to keep scripts parametric and easy to adjust
Each script should be fully self-contained: clear the scene, build the model, set up basic materials, and position at world origin
Keep poly count game-appropriate — use modifiers for detail rather than dense geometry
Include a comment block at the top of each script with the key parameters (span width, height, arch radius etc.) so they are easy to find and tweak
